  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/video/\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd-\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8-\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd-\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd-\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe/52-300635",
  "time_ut": 1658126115,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Will bus fares decrease due to lower fuel prices?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Private bus associations say they are ready to revise bus fares due to the reduction in fuel prices.",
        "Anjana Priyanjith, Secretary of All Sri Lanka Private Bus Owners Association, said that this stage of revision should be carried out as per the national policy.",
        "He said that if the price of diesel increases or decreases by 4% as stated in the National Bus Fare Policy, there is definitely a possibility to revise the bus fare.",
        "Meanwhile, Chairman of Sri Lanka Private Bus Owners Association Kemunu Wijeratne has said that he is ready to reduce the bus fare if fuel is provided properly."
      ],
